div.div:
I, the protagonist, was just an ordinary high school girl, but suddenly I was reincarnated as a spider monster in a fantasy world. Not only that, but I awakened in a dungeon filled with vicious monsters. Armed with only my human knowledge and my overwhelming positivity, I'm forced to use spiderwebs and traps to defeat far stronger monsters just to stay alive... So begins the labyrinth survival story of a girl with incredible mental strength living as one of the lowest-ranked beasts!
(Source: Crunchyroll)

The third season of Log Horizon. It’s been a year since Shiroe and his friends were trapped in Akiba due to the Catastrophe. Their forging of the Round Table has brought order and prosperity to its people. But fracturing political alliances and the constant menace of the Genius monsters threaten to destabilize all they’ve fought for and built. Can faith be restored and they persevere, or is its destruction truly inevitable? (Source: Funimation)
Enzai de Shokei Sareta Koushaku Reijou wa Konse de wa Mofu Kami-sama to Odayaka ni Sugoshitai
Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life, Supernatural

Catriona Julie Grande, the daughter of a marquis, was the Crown Prince’s fiancee. She was executed under false charges but went back in time. All she wanted was to live her life peacefully and prevent the same tragic fate from occurring again. But one day, the Prince appears in her life again and everything begins to fall apart. She has no idea what to do!
(Source: MangaUpates)
Ikidaore mo Dekinai Konna Isekai ja
Comedy, Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life

Sumire was a high school girl before she leapt into another world the moment she fell down. Before she could collapse and die, she came across a silver-haired boy who had already collapsed and was dying. One thing led to another and she ended up working at an Adventurer’s Guild. She doesn’t have any special powers, but she’s well liked by strange plants and animals. What does Sumire’s future hold?!
